api_list.name: Get Astro Photo Info (randomly)
api_list.description: Return one of the photo info selected randomly by system, including paths (image_hd and image) which use to download photo in **Download Astro Photo** method.
api_list.code:
import requests

url = "https://astro-gallery.p.rapidapi.com/get_astro_photo_info"

headers = {
            "X-RapidAPI-Key": "SIGN-UP-FOR-KEY",
            "X-RapidAPI-Host": "astro-gallery.p.rapidapi.com"
        }

response = requests.get(url, headers=headers)
print(response.json())
